result.name: Ming Garden Restaurant

reviews.text: tasty food. a wide range choice. reasonable price but some staff's manner is not positive

Top Restaurant in HK  up in the mall nearby n close the the Dorsett Hotel. Excellent service n top chef's created a banquet fit for a King ..... i like to give the Manager a Thankyou for his exceptional service in making our dinner with our HK family an enjoyable experience to remember we ate Roast Suckling Pig ..Roast Goose (Very popular here in HK ..it taste like duck but more meatier n less fat) ..n we also had Ginger n Shallot Steamed Fish ....straight out of the fishtank like it was just caught out of the ocean ...Take your family take your friends have a feast ....Enjoy !! 👍👍👍🍺🍺🍺 Have a beer as well Cheers !

Very nice dim sum restaurant serving very high quality Cantonese cuisine and modern dim sum. I found the atmosphere, decorations as well as service is very pleasant and is definitely good for business lunch and friends and family gathering. It is one of my favorite place for dim sum lunch with family and sometimes for dinner gathering with friends. If I need a place serving above average Cantonese food this is one of the best options.
Foods and service are good but a bit pricey.
nice environment and service.....Not too crowded on Sunday night

reviews.text: 食物質數和價錢都比一般連鎖酒家高一點，性價比正常，可以的。
招呼一時時，唔係熟客唔多理你。其實食物十分有水準，價位可能覺得高些，不過味道搭夠。
食肆整潔 水滚茶香 服務好 旧客離新客坐枱布換 舒適
點心好食，早上十一㸃半埋單有折價，抵食。
